Dear Investor,

*Tamar Marash*

We are delighted to announce that we are conducting our first closing of
ALF III fund, the 3rd series of Funds in our Global Asset Based Lending
Strategy with total committed and investable capital of $480M at closing.

As a reminder, ALF III funds seek to provide investors with attractive
ongoing current income and potential for capital gains through asset-based
lending transactions to finance assets originated by Tech enabled Lenders
(aka FinTech lenders) across US, Western Europe, U.K and Australia.

We are also excited to draw your attention to the first capital call
following the execution of our first transactions in ALF III fund.
Please see attached the capital call letter, wire instructions and the
fund=E2=80=99s tax withholding exemption (relevant for Israeli investors).

We wanted to take this opportunity to thank you all for the continued trust
and support and looking forward for a fruitful partnership.

Thank you,
Viola Credit Management Team

